author: Christian Datoc
title: ‘SpongeBob’ Crashes MSNBC Live Shot Outside Trump Tower [VIDEO]
text:
TOP 5420266 
A man wearing a SpongeBob SquarePants t-shirt interrupted Hallie Jackson’s Thursday afternoon report from outside Trump Tower in New York City. 
WATCH: 
“Hillary is running Pizzagate!” the apparent-Nickelodeon fan shouted. “Hillary is running a child sex trafficking ring!” 
MSNBC was forced to prematurely end Jackson’s segment with a quick clarification from host Steve Kornacki. 
“Alright Hallie Jackson outside of Trump Tower,” he told viewers. “You never know who you might run into there.”
